{
  "id": "RAW_20e84719",
  "title": "AI 垃圾内容、生产力，以及为什么 AI 驱动的世界不会飞速前进",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/slop-productivity-and-why-the-ai",
  "date": "2026-06-07 23:31:43",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p>Just saw a graph at the FT from John Burn-Murdoch that really distills something I have been trying to articulate. AI generates a lot of output (which fits many people’s informal notion of productivity), but it hasn’t yielded much in the way of RoI for many companies (per studies from MIT, McKinsey, Bain, and many others), and hasn’t materially changed GDP.</p>\n   <p><span>The particular graph from the FT happens to be about mobile apps (h/t </span><a href=\"https://x.com/jenzhuscott/status/2063032701087883647?s=61\">Jen Zhu</a><span>). But you could make similar graphs in many domains: loads of nominal productivity, but not much real world impact.</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b078b11d-edce-4f2b-43cb-f5116d46d700/public\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1315,&quot;width&quot;:1115,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:898590,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/200893787?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a6f5e868-fec6-4e84-9b90-8dd615606a00/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_0c2ecf00-3c9f-40e4-a8cf-b6e4168a2fb3_1115x1315.png 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b078b11d-edce-4f2b-43cb-f5116d46d700/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>You could, for example, say something similar about books. GenAI has led to a lot more books, but it’s not clear that they are better books or (sorry I don’t have the data immediately available) more books sold. Here are numbers of books available over time, from </span><a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2026/05/20/data-shows-that-ai-slop-is-taking-over-books-lawsuits-music-science/\">The Washington Post</a><span>:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1628,&quot;width&quot;:1442,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:339863,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/200893787?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_127f7742-4e48-43c4-beb9-af234f5c5622_1442x1628.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>Book sales, on the other hand, </span><a href=\"https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/industry-news/financial-reporting/article/99417-print-book-sales-rose-slightly-in-2025.html\">have declined slightly over the same period</a><span>. And I don’t hear any argument that books are getting </span><em>better</em><span>. </span></p>\n   <p>The Post article that I drew the above from had similar graphs for the rise in music tracks uploaded, self-represented lawsuits filed, scientific papers submitted, and web content generated.</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ed63199f-4f06-4223-e025-bd290b5bda00/public 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1503,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:204342,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/200893787?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/20d28fb9-fb73-4715-5786-bb46a22bb800/public 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_f1cbc5c6-b0f4-414b-ad33-3c3d10c6a7c7_1534x1584.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>Again there is no reason to think that any of it has added to the GDP or quality of science or music. Most of it is slop (and in some cases </span><a href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/why-is-the-roi-on-generative-ai-so?utm_source=publication-search\">work slop</a><span>):</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:505,&quot;width&quot;:1332,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:152396,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/200893787?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f511614-9ccb-4362-a2a8-f2f4002befd8_1340x790.jpeg&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_7ba22eca-8e9b-45db-ad49-c3e7d4a6084d_1332x505.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>The graphs from FT and The Washington Post show the same thing over and over; we are being flooded with AI-generated content, from apps to music to scientific papers, but that doesn’t make any of it any good. Most of it (in fairness, not all) isn’t.</p>\n   <p><span>And then you have </span><a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2025/08/08/wikipedia-ai-generated-mistakes-editors/\">slop inundating Wikipedia</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://lithub.com/libraries-are-already-contending-with-crappy-ai-generated-books/\">libraries</a><span> and so on.</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:845,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:116245,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/200893787?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260607170259_e9805b08-4a18-4022-8ee0-fcca4f0f2a23_1491x865.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>It is very likely that the same thing is happening in math. A group of mathematicians, who are fearful about many aspects of the impact of AI on math research, have written an open letter called the “</span><a href=\"https://leidendeclaration.ai/\">Leiden Declaration</a><span>”, </span><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/science/ai-mathematics-leiden-declaration.html\">reported by the NYT</a><span>, expressing (among other concerns) their fear that </span></p>\n   <p><em>Current automated techniques can produce plausible but unreliable (or even incorrect) arguments which are difficult to distinguish from correct mathematical proofs. This applies not only to informal arguments, but also to formalizations, where the difficulty lies in the translation between computer-encoded and human presentations of concepts. These fast-moving developments put our present system of review under increasing pressure, jeopardizing our ability to implement traditional standards for the correctness, transparency, and independent verifiability of proof.</em></p>\n   <p>In other words, math slop.</p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\">\n     <div class=\"container-IpPqBD\">\n      <form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" novalidate class=\"form form-M5sC90\">\n       <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\">\n       <div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\">\n        <div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative pc-reset flex-auto-j3S2WA\">\n          <input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\">\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"submit\" disabled class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button>\n       </div>\n      </form>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p>Not long ago, when I was thinking about the official productivity measures and whether they would change with AI, an investor friend wrote to remind me how narrow the technical definition of productivity with respect to GDP is, noting that “In the technical world of national accounting, paying people to dig and refill holes adds to GDP.”</p>\n   <p>Using GenAI runs up tokens costs, and floods the world with content. But all too often that content — created by a giant but unreliable word prediction machine that is more regurgitative than innovative — is of little lasting value.</p>\n   <p><em>Maybe</em><span> the biggest exception is coding, but even there, it’s not yet clear how many of the systems that have been created with the help of agentic coding will endure. </span></p>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p><span>Moreover, especially in agentic coding, there are </span><em>massive</em><span> losses, up and down the food chain. The providers (Open AI, Anthropic, Cursor, etc) lose tons of money, and are scrambling to raise prices, Customers are balking at the new usage models.(In a new analysis, Gerben Wierda has argued that Anthropic and OpenAI “</span><a href=\"https://ea.rna.nl/2026/06/07/anthropic-openai-may-be-spending-more-than-1000-for-every-100-you-pay-them/\">may actually pay $1000 for every $100 you pay them</a><span>”. Data center intermediaries like CoreWeave are also losing money. It’s hard even to say how the chip companies are doing, once you factor out all the circular financing and shrinking cash flow. The one possible major productivity story (coding) also happens to be the one burning the most cash. </span></p>\n   <p><span>It could well be that once the providers (Open AI, Anthropic, Cursor, etc) attempt to charge enough money to cover their losses, </span><a href=\"https://www.inc.com/joe-procopio/ai-is-now-more-expensive-than-the-mass-layoff-human-labor-its-replacing/91356134\">the cost of AI could become more expensive than the humans it is replacing</a><span>. </span></p>\n   <p>Talk about digging holes without creating real value.</p>\n   <p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/slop-productivity-and-why-the-ai?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/slop-productivity-and-why-the-ai?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\" class=\"button primary\"><span>Share</span></a></p>\n   <p><span>PS. See also </span><span style=\"min-width:0;\" data-state=\"closed\"><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/users/26817325-paul-krugman?utm_source=mentions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Paul Krugman&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:26817325,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;user&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cd097e5-2750-4a19-aaf3-6425407e9b6c_951x951.jpeg&quot;,&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;82025fa7-da11-416a-afec-16ba7a26c229&quot;}\" data-component-name=\"MentionUser\" class=\"mention-pnpTE1\">Paul Krugman</a></span><span> and </span><a href=\"https://paulkedrosky.com/the-return-of-sloc/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email\">Paul Kedrosky</a><span> for new pieces reaching somewhat similar conclusions, from different angles.</span></p>\n   <p>PPS Apropos tweet, tongue presumably partly in cheek, from yesterday:</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/yuchenj_uw/status/2063315896421274076?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/yuchenj_uw/status/2063315896421274076?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Before AI, I’d spend a weekend building 1 useless app.\\n\\nNow I can build 67 useless apps over a weekend, each with a logo, a fancy webpage, and 0 user.&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;Yuchenj_UW&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Yuchen Jin&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1319081238439751681/kCcqnwoF_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-06-06T17:43:38.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:95,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:39,&quot;like_count&quot;:788,&quot;impression_count&quot;:22786,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @Yuchenj_UW\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f31e7c-aa17-427e-d09b-e9cef7da4600/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260405170507_kCcqnwoF.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Yuchen Jin</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@Yuchenj_UW</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Before AI, I’d spend a weekend building 1 useless app. Now I can build 67 useless apps over a weekend, each with a logo, a fancy webpage, and 0 user.</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">5:43 PM · Jun 6, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">22.8K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">95 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">39 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">788 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文认为，尽管 AI 生成的内容在应用、书籍、音乐和科学领域大量涌现，但其对现实世界的经济和质量的实质性影响仍然微乎其微，大部分内容都是低质量的“垃圾内容”，而主要的 AI 提供商正在烧钱。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文认为，尽管 AI 生成的内容在应用、书籍、音乐和科学领域大量涌现，但其对现实世界的经济和质量的实质性影响仍然微乎其微，大部分内容都是低质量的“垃圾内容”，而主要的 AI 提供商正在烧钱。",
  "summary": "Gary Marcus 综合了来自《金融时报》、《华盛顿邮报》等来源的数据，论证了生成式 AI 虽然极大地增加了内容（应用、书籍、音乐曲目、科学论文和法律文件）的数量，但并未带来质量、销售额或 GDP 的相应增长。他引入了“垃圾内容”这一概念来描述这种低价值的产出。文章进一步将批评延伸到智能体编程领域，指出尽管这可能是最有希望的生产力用例，但它也是资金消耗最密集的领域，像 OpenAI 和 Anthropic 这样的提供商可能亏损远超其收入。Marcus 总结道，AI 行业有制造一场空洞繁荣的风险，即产生了活动却没有持久价值，并警告说 AI 的成本可能很快就会超过它所取代的人力劳动。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 极大地增加了产出数量，但没有增加实际价值或 GDP。",
      "explanation": "来自《金融时报》和《华盛顿邮报》的数据显示，AI 生成的应用、书籍、音乐和论文数量激增，但图书销量却下降了，且对 GDP 没有影响。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大多数 AI 生成的内容都是“垃圾内容”——看似合理但不可靠，且几乎没有持久价值。",
      "explanation": "Marcus 认为，大型语言模型是“巨大但不可靠的词语预测机器”，它们产生的是重复性的内容，从维基百科到科学出版领域都充斥着这类内容。"
    },
    {
      "point": "最有希望的 AI 生产力故事——智能体编程，正在烧掉大量资金。",
      "explanation": "像 OpenAI 和 Anthropic 这样的提供商，每获得 100 美元收入，可能就要花费超过 1000 美元，而提价的尝试又遭到客户抵制，这威胁到了整个产业链的经济可行性。"
    }
  ],
